reviewText: I bought this for my son for Christmas. He loves all of the George Shrinks cartoons. I like this DVD because it has three episodes of GS and a bonus seven little monsters, and we like that cartoon too.

My kids love to watch this series, so I was very excited to buy this!  They watch it at least once a week, but it's so good for them.  It is a PBS show!  George is so very independent, but still helps his family out, which is great for kids to see!

The DVD has 2 episodes:
Snowman's land
From bad to worse
and 1 bonus episode from 7 little monsters series
